{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to &quot;Before Fate&quot;: A Nexus of Time and Space</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cBefore Fate\u201d blends retro sci-fi with imaginative comic art for a unique survival adventure. Journey through time portals, explore diverse worlds, gather resources, face survival challenges, explore mysterious dungeons, and gradually uncover the truth behind an interstellar disaster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Time-Space Odyssey:</strong>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore diverse environments, from desolate deserts to mysterious forests. Each realm hides uncharted challenges and wonders. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u8dc3\u8fc1\u65f6\u7a7a601X258_5M.gif?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Deep Narrative:</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Trace the enigmatic path of the Chrono Gem, collaborate with scientists from the Aude Research Institute to unlock the secrets of the universe and avert impending disasters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u6df1\u5ea6\u5267\u60c5601X258_5M.gif?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rich Arsenal:</strong>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft your combat style with over a hundred types of weapons and numerous unique items, coloring each expedition with uniqueness. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u88c5\u5907\u4e30\u5bcc601X258_5M.gif?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzle Challenges:</strong>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Integrate intuitive UI with environmental interactions, where each puzzle sharpens your wit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u89e3\u8c1c\u6311\u6218601X258.gif?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tribute to Classics:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every frame pays homage to the modern reinterpretation of classics, saluting masters like Moebius. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u7075\u611f\u4e4b\u4f5c601X258.gif?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Artistic Style:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Retro Meets Modern:</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A blend of '70s and '80s sci-fi with comic styles, each pixel radiates with retro-futuristic charm.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hand-Drawn World:</strong>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carefully crafted scenes and characters depict a vibrant world brimming with life and imagination. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u5206\u5272\u6bb5\u843d601X258_5M.gif?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Story Overview:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;The Nexus is a point where time and space converge, revealing endless possibilities and hopes. It is as brief and brilliant as a shooting star.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In an era where robots coexist with humans, a meteor\u2019s descent forebodes looming catastrophes. As scientist Ian Stewart, alongside the leader of the Aude team, Abel Morrison, venture into the marvel of time and space, exploring, battling, and unveiling the mysteries of the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u5206\u5272\u56fe\u72472_601.png?t=1735119434\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cross the veil of time, explore endless possibilities, and make &quot;Before Fate&quot; your journey through time and space. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join us in unraveling the world of &quot;Before Fate&quot;!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/extras/\u5206\u5272\u56fe\u72471_601.png?t=1735119434\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735119434","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/page.bg.jpg?t=1735119434","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/4e94cf8e48c8745df0bbe5431c95437d50fb0f75/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735119434","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866920/4e94cf8e48c8745df0bbe5431c95437d50fb0f75/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735119434","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2055350,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to &quot;Before Fate&quot;: A Nexus of Time and Spac